[{"Id": 1015009, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": "Also quoted from Mujtana, a man is reported to have seen the Holy Prophet (s) in dream and asked him to teach him a supplicatory prayer that would refresh his heart. Therefore, the Holy Prophet (s) taught him these words. The man commented, When I repeated these words 3 times, Almighty Allah refreshed my heart…", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Kitaab Mujtana mein hi mazkoor hai keh ek shakhs ne Hazrat Rasool-e-Khuda (s) ko khwaab mein dekha to Aan Hazrat (s) se darkhwaast ki keh mujhe aisi dua taaleem farmaye keh jis se mera dil zindah ho jaaye, pas Huzoor-e-Akram (s) ne usey yeh kalemaat taaleem farmaye. Woh shakhs bayaan karta hai keh mai ne yeh kalemaat 3 martaba kahe to Allah Taala ne mere dil ko zindah kar diya…", "UrduDescription": "کتاب مجتنیٰ ہی میں مذکور ہے کہ ایک شخص نے حضرت رسول اﷲؐکو خواب میں دیکھا تو حضرت سے درخواست کی : مجھے ایسی دعا تعلیم فرمائیے کہ جس سے میرا دل زندہ ہو جائے پس حضور اکرم ؐ نے اسے یہ کلمات تعلیم فرمائے۔۔۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": nul